color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Arial Unicode MS","sans-serif";
color:black'>Algae, which can be grown using waste materials such as sewage and
without displacing land currently used for food production;</span></p>



<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
